Package: dnsforge
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Declarative DNS zone manager with Rhai scripting
 Dnsforge manages DNS zones declaratively using Rhai scripts.
 It fetches current zone state via AXFR, computes a diff against
 the desired state, and applies changes via RFC 2136 dynamic
 updates with TSIG authentication.
